1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,158
When you start the activities, they will follow the same order as this lesson.

2
00:00:05,108 --> 00:00:12,635
First, you do a warm-up: Pick a meaningful name such as shopping list, appointment note or my practice note.

3
00:00:12,635 --> 00:00:17,214
Then you answer quick checks, so we know the key words make sense.

4
00:00:17,214 --> 00:00:26,779
Next, you practise the real computer skill: Open Word, type one sentence, use Save As, type the file name and choose Documents.

5
00:00:26,779 --> 00:00:32,092
You may also type a short answer, for example: Type a clear file name.

6
00:00:32,092 --> 00:00:39,239
At the end, you finish with a stretch or reflection: Use Save As to make a second copy with a different name.

7
00:00:39,239 --> 00:00:42,632
Talk about when two versions might be useful.

8
00:00:42,632 --> 00:00:45,159
Take one activity at a time.

9
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:49,701
If you need help, ask staff, then try the next step yourself.

